                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>12.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Reconnect conn. (182), and at (J7)/(181) circuit 56H, measure voltage to ground.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>(181), 56H to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>Pulsating 12 &#177; 1.5 volts.</para>
