                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>F15, 12A to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>12 &#177; 1.5 volts.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Locate cause of low or no voltage in circuit 12 or 12A, then repair.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>19.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>At (J7)/(181) terminal 5, measure voltage to ground.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>(181), term. 5 to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>12 &#177; 1.5 volts</para>
