                            <para>Locate cause of low or no voltage in circuit 12F, then repair.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>24.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>At (J7)/(181) measure voltage from terminal 7 to 8.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>(181), term. 7 to 8.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>12 &#177; 1.5 volts.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Locate open or poor connection in circuit 11-GR to cab ground, then repair.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>25.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>At relay socket (179) measure voltage from circuit 12F to 11-GS.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>(179), 12F to 11-GS.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>12 &#177; 1.5 volts.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Locate open or poor connection in circuit 11-GS, then repair.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>26.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>With key switch in accessory or on position, at (179) measure voltage from circuit 12E
                                to 11-GS.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>(179), 12E to 11-GS.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>12 &#177; 1.5 volts.</para>
                        </entry>
